      set:html={isEnglish
        ? `Diagnosis is based on:<br/><br/>
      <strong class='text-white'>Physical examination:</strong> Where mobility, muscle strength, and reflexes are evaluated.<br/><br/>
      <strong class='text-white'>Imaging studies:</strong> Studies such as X-rays, MRIs, and CT scans allow confirmation of the diagnosis, evaluation of stenosis (number of compression levels, importance and location of stenosis, and associated instability).`
